title: [Rozy's Magic Shoppe]
description: Enclosed by white silk-paneled walls, the shop features a glass-fronted bookcase in the center of its patterned floor.  A wrinkled parchment gown pattern hangs under the vaulted ceiling.  Right near the front is a heavy lead glass display case and a silk-covered dress mannequin.

White silk-paneled walls rise from an intricate patterned floor.  Just above a glass-fronted bookcase hangs a wrinkled parchment gown pattern, and a glass-tiled vaulted ceiling completes the picture.  A heavy lead glass display case and a silk-covered dress mannequin stand side by side in the middle of the room.
